<!DOCTYPE html>
<html class='no-js' lang='en'>
  <head>
    <meta charset='utf-8'>
    <meta content='IE=edge,chrome=1' http-equiv='X-UA-Compatible'>
    <title>Solda</title>
    <link href='stylesheets/style.css' rel='stylesheet'>
  </head>
  <body id="page-store">

    <header class="profile">
      <img src="images/store/logo.png" class="seller-avatar" alt="">
      <h1>UNIFORM WARE 之高速潮男</h1>
      <p class="stats">
        100 % 好評 • 310 追蹤 • 52 件商品
      </p>
      <p class="about-preview">
        為週末台北人安排的各種都市生活圈旅行，希望你能夠好放鬆，享受自然給人的療癒。 <a href="#" class="show-more">...關於我</a>
      </p>
      <p>
        <a href="#" class="follow">追蹤我</a>
      </p>
    </header>
    
    <section class="about-full">
      <h1>關於我</h1>
      <p><%= jp_lorem_sentences(8) %></p>
      <p class="store-info">
        營業時間：平日 10AM - 6PM <br> 中山北路二段103號8樓
      </p>
      <p class="social-links">
        <a href="#">Website</a>
        <a href="#">Phone</a>
        <a href="#">Facebook</a>
        <a href="#">Twitter</a>
      </p>
      <hr>
      <p class="ratings-overview">
        已經累積 23 個好評，好評率 98%。
      </p>
      <p class="ratings">
        <strong class="good">Good<br><span>23</span></strong>
        <strong class="okay">Okay<br><span>5</span></strong>
        <strong class="bad">Bad<br><span>1</span></strong>
      </p>
    </section>
    
    <section class="broadcast">
	  <p><%= jp_lorem_sentences(8) %></p>      
    </section>
    
    <section class="tags">
      <a href="#" class="current">全部商品</a>
      <% 14.times do %>
      <a href="#"><%= lorem_word %></a>
      <% end %>
    </section>
    
    <section class="products">
	  <p><%= jp_lorem_sentences(8) %></p>      
    </section>


  </body>
</html>
